README

HW4
by Brian Salmon

It took about 4 hours

Instructions:

Change the rotation with arrow keys

'Esc' will close the window

'a' to toggle axis

'0' to reset view angle

‘m’ to toggle between orthogonal and perspective

‘f’ to change to first person

‘w/s’ to move forward/backward in first person

‘a/d’ to rotate camera in first person

Page up and down to zoom in and out